        {
            "title": "歐協聯｜車路士力爭成首支贏盡歐戰所有錦標球隊",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"車路士力爭成首支贏盡歐戰所有錦標球隊。REUTERS/新華社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6f07b7cc1665f82338d45f3dc04deab7/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250509/_2025050913494726867.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">車路士力爭成首支贏盡歐戰所有錦標球隊。REUTERS/新華社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>車路士淘汰佐加頓斯闖進歐協聯決賽，將與西甲的貝迪斯爭奪錦標。藍獅主帥馬列斯卡指打入決賽對球隊意義重大，因為他們只要擊敗貝迪斯捧盃，便可以成為史上首支贏盡所有歐戰錦標的球隊。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士打入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3dd2072f61e95a2aa535a722ed8d53a5/2025-05/2025-05-08T194410Z_1585816795_UP1EL581ITKTI_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-CHE-DIF-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士打入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士打入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/59791ff6bf0d30a4fa3c7d237984e0ae/2025-05/2025-05-08T201730Z_1554045595_UP1EL581KD4UF_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-CHE-DIF-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士打入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士領隊馬列斯卡在場邊十分緊張。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f4ff5224cde68a63f2f53865ef7afda8/2025-05/2025-05-08T203848Z_1973220062_UP1EL581LCMVT_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-CHE-DIF-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士領隊馬列斯卡在場邊十分緊張。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士(藍衫)打入歐協聯決賽。AP\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f00026dbeb64353bc3d0bf90b52db6f5/2025-05/Britain_Soccer_Europa_Conference_League_31972--6ab3d.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士(藍衫)打入歐協聯決賽。AP\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士(右)打入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2aedf2e63acbc492383ad1685d747fb8/2025-05/Britain_Soccer_Europa_Conference_League_99509--9b7ed.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士(右)打入歐協聯決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車路士球迷歡呼慶祝球隊入決賽。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/66a1f0b71a41757dcf64f39a22ed5da2/2025-05/2025-05-08T210819Z_1360364006_UP1EL581MPTXD_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-CONFERENCE-CHE-DIF-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車路士球迷歡呼慶祝球隊入決賽。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>馬列斯卡：歐協聯對球會意義重大</h2>\n<p>歐協聯在2021才成立，今屆才是第4屆，之前只有羅馬、韋斯咸和奧林比亞高斯贏過冠軍。所以，若車路士在決賽擊敗貝迪斯捧盃，便可以成為史上首支集齊歐聯、歐霸、歐洲盃賽冠軍盃、歐洲超級盃和歐協盃所有歐洲足協舉辦的球會賽錦標。馬列斯卡亦矢言要帶領藍獅創造歷史：「對我們來說，打入決賽意義重大。因為車路士有機會成為第一家贏盡所有歐戰冠軍的球會，這是我們的首要奮鬥目標。我們能夠一路闖進決賽，過程殊不簡單，從球隊建設的角度，這場決事亦十分重要。歐協聯就是我們再創高峰的一個起點，我們希望藉這項錦標逐步建立勝利者的心態，從而再爭取更高的錦標。」\n\n</p><h2>古斯圖：全力備戰決賽</h2>\n<p>車路士後衛馬路古斯圖和應道：「我們若成功奪冠，便可以成為歐洲第一家贏盡所有歐戰冠軍的球會，這是很多球會都夢寐以求的成就，意義十分重大。對球隊、球員、球迷，都是很高的榮譽。所以，我們在球季餘下時間要盡全力備戰這場決賽。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2068064/即時-體育-歐協聯-車路士力爭成首支贏盡歐戰所有錦標球隊",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-09 14:01:31",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
